invalid type: string "Pottery factory is made \nentirely by hand. From the \npreparation of the clay \nthrough to the glazing and \npainting of each piece, \neverything is made just \nas it was in 1741, the year \nin which the factory was \nfounded.\nThe result of a centuries-\nold traditional Portuguese \nart, Sant’Anna pottery \nand tiles are renowned \nas products of quality \ns \n2\no \nm \n